First-class.matches: 169CricInfo and CricketArchive disagree over the number of matches Bennett played. The CricInfo total of 169 has been used here as the site is not behind a paywall. CricketArchive provides a total of 170 matches. Runs scored and wickets taken are identical for both sources.
deliveries: Due to incomplete scorecards from the mid-19th century, the number of balls bowled and bowling average are approximate
